
Bloodfist Help:  Stun

Guild level:  5
Honor Req:    0
Base Cost:    27

  Stun your opponent with a powerful blow, removing yourself and your
target from combat.  Your target's attacker will stop attacking, however
if it has multiple attackers then fighting will still continue even
after you have removed yourself from the fight.

Usage:  stun
        stun <who>

